question.title: JRuby Google App Engine throws sun.misc.Unsafe is a restricted class for new Rails App

node.contents: I'm trying to get a new JRuby Rails Application to run on Google App Engine. I keep getting a sun.misc.Unsafe is a restricted class error when I try to run it.

astNode.text: I'm trying to get a new JRuby Rails Application to run on Google App Engine. I keep getting a sun.misc.Unsafe is a restricted class error when I try to run it.

node.contents: Does anyone know what is causing this?
